@startuml sequence_search
!theme plain
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title Vector Search

actor User
participant "Angular" as SPA
participant "POST /api/search" as API
participant "IEmbeddingClient" as EC
participant "AppDbContext" as CTX
database "pgvector HNSW" as DB
participant "Provider" as P

User -> SPA: submit query
SPA -> API: POST /api/search { q }
API -> API: validate q, rate limit
API -> EC: EmbedAsync(q)
EC -> P: POST /embeddings
P --> EC: float[1536]
EC --> API: qv
API -> CTX: SqlQuery<Row>(CTE)
CTX -> DB: WITH contact_hits ... ORDER BY similarity
DB --> CTX: ranked rows (best per contact)
CTX --> API: rows
API -> API: trim matchedText to 240 chars
API --> SPA: SearchResponse
SPA --> User: results list

@enduml
